tr.th: Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us

tr.td: All measured parameters are within normal limits except for a mildly elevated HbA1c (6.2%), indicating impaired glucose metabolism or possible prediabetes. Renal function, electrolytes, and glucose are normal. Recommend clinical follow-up for glycemic control and assessment for diabetes risk factors.
